nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.dataset

Class Dataset<TData,TTarget extends Target<? extends TData>>

  • nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.dataset.Dataset<TData,TTarget>
  • Type Parameters:
    TData -

    The type of the features in the input vector.

    TTarget -

    The type of the outputs in the input vector.


    public class Dataset<TData,TTarget extends Target<? extends TData>>

    A basic data set composed of a vector of input class Samples and a collection of output interface Targets.

    NOTE: The type of the inputs and outputs is constrained to be the same.

    See Also:
    class Sample, interface Target

        A basic data set composed of a vector of input class Samples and a collection of output interface Targets.

        NOTE: The type of the inputs and outputs is constrained to be the same.

        Parameters:
        inputs - Vector of inputs with the shape [samples, features].
        outputs - Vector that describes target values for each sample in the input vector, with shape [samples].
